markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>收购花旗财富后汇丰银行在华员工人数增加300多人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-adds-over-300-china-headcount-after-citi-wealth-acquisition-2024-06-11/</link><description>汇丰银行周二表示，随着这家专注于亚洲的银行完成了对花旗集团在全球第二大经济体的消费者财富投资组合的收购，该银行已将其在中国的员工人数增加了300多人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-adds-over-300-china-headcount-after-citi-wealth-acquisition-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟政治搅乱市场情绪，亚洲股市持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-11/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市情绪谨慎，因右翼在选举中获胜以及法国提前民意调查重新引发了人们对欧盟凝聚力的担忧，投资者开始思考欧洲市场新的政治不确定性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>英国将针对中国和香港的司法影响力“武器化”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uk-weaponising-judicial-influence-against-china-hong-kong-says-city-leader-2024-06-11/</link><description>香港特首李家超周二表示，在两名英国法官从香港最高法院辞职后，英国正在将其对中国和香港的司法影响力武器化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/uk-weaponising-judicial-influence-against-china-hong-kong-says-city-leader-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>台湾逮捕快艇闯入台北港的前中国海军舰长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-arrests-former-chinese-navy-captain-whose-speedboat-entered-taipei-2024-06-11/</link><description>台湾高级官员周二表示，一名因快艇非法进入台北港而被捕的中国男子是一名前海军上尉，他可能正在探测该岛的防御工事。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-arrests-former-chinese-navy-captain-whose-speedboat-entered-taipei-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国媒体和官员称，四名美国教育工作者在中国东北公园被刺伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/four-american-educators-stabbed-park-northeast-china-says-us-media-officials-2024-06-11/</link><description>据美国媒体和美国政府官员称，周一，来自爱荷华州一所小型大学的四名美国教育工作者在中国东北吉林省一个公园发生的持刀袭击事件中受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/four-american-educators-stabbed-park-northeast-china-says-us-media-officials-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国在朝鲜越过边境后鸣枪警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-fired-warning-shots-weekend-after-border-incursion-2024-06-11/</link><description>首尔官员表示，周末一些朝鲜士兵短暂越过边境后，韩国军方鸣枪示警，平壤最近因向韩国发射气球运载垃圾而导致紧张局势升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-fired-warning-shots-weekend-after-border-incursion-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>关键通胀测试前美元坚挺；日本央行会议前夕日元疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-key-inflation-test-fed-forecast-update-2024-06-11/</link><description>周二，美元兑欧元徘徊在一个月高点附近，兑日元升至一周高点，交易员为第二天关键的美国通胀数据和美联储新利率预测做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:24:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-key-inflation-test-fed-forecast-update-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>在中国，对身份的追求推动了高端运动服饰品牌 Lululemon 的发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-search-identity-boosts-lululemon-premium-sportswear-brands-2024-06-11/</link><description>高端运动服饰品牌在中国正享受着强劲的增长，因为它们开始直接吸引主要客户，这给大品牌耐克和阿迪达斯在价值 550 亿美元的运动服饰市场与本土竞争对手的竞争中带来了又一次挫折。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 01:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-search-identity-boosts-lululemon-premium-sportswear-brands-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，菲律宾必须做好应对外部威胁增长的准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-must-prepare-external-threat-now-more-worrisome-president-says-2024-06-11/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，由于印太地区紧张局势加剧，外部威胁更加明显，菲律宾应该为任何可能发生的情况做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-must-prepare-external-threat-now-more-worrisome-president-says-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：行业官员表示，越南多年来首次允许企业进口黄金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-let-companies-import-gold-first-time-years-industry-official-says-2024-06-10/</link><description>一位行业官员告诉路透社，越南预计将在十多年来首次允许企业进口黄金，其目的是缩小当地价格与国际基准之间不断扩大的差距。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 23:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-let-companies-import-gold-first-time-years-industry-official-says-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：等待游戏，日本骚动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>